@startuml
title Exercise 4.3 - Lab Inventory RMI Architecture

actor "User" as user
participant "EquipmentRmiClient" as client
participant "RMI Registry\n(:24000)" as registry
participant "EquipmentServiceImpl" as server
database "EquipmentRepository\n(in memory)" as repo

user -> client : types command + equipment code
client -> registry : lookup("equipmentService")
registry --> client : remote stub
client -> server : consultarEquipos()\nreservarEquipo(code)
server -> repo : query/modify
repo --> server : result
server --> client : String / boolean
client --> user : display result

legend right
  4 operations: list/consult/reserve/release
  Java-only (RMI)
endlegend

@enduml